    body
        !{locals.header}
        div(id="head-gradient" class="text-center head-gradient-blue")
            div(class="display-3") HarmoniCraft Staff Portal
            h3 A portal to find what you need 
        div(class = "container-fluid")
            div(class = "row")
                div(class="col-minimal")
                div(class="col-xl")
                    h1(class = "text-center") General
                    img(class = "mx-auto d-block" src = "images/1.png")
                    p(class = "text-center") Important, general purpose links
                    div(class = "mx-auto w100")
                        a(href = "https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/104BVvjpmAmF2PHF5TPDcIWtcpkYnjGCAoo-bL7drugU/edit?usp=sharing" target = "_blank" class = "header") Staff List
                        ul
                            li View staff members and their ranks
                            li View contact information of each member
                            li Find information about extra positions
                            
                        a(href = "http://harmonicraft.com/rules" target = "_blank" class = "header") Harmonicraft Rules
                        ul
                            li Also found on website
                            
                        a(href = "http://harmonicraft.com/forum/m/27942449/viewforum/5439296" target = "_blank" class = "header") Staff Forums
                        ul
                            li Also found on website
                    br
                    
                div(class="col-xl")
                    h1(class = "text-center") Helper Help
                    img(class = "mx-auto d-block" src = "images/2.png")
                    p(class = "text-center" class = "text-center") Advice for incoming, or current helpers
                    div(class = "mx-auto w100")
                        div
                            a(href = "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1b485j2I6RkpqJy7yFyp0YvPMhFl91kHU11_NulWu0Qc/edit" target = "_blank" class = "header") Staff Guidelines
                            ul
                                li Make sure to be familiar with the expectations here
                                
                            a(href = "http://harmonicraft.com/wiki/m/35041432/page/Editing_The_Wiki" target = "_blank" class = "header") Editing the Wiki
                            ul
                                li A guide on how to make good contributions to the wiki
                            
                    br
                    
                div(class="col-xl")
                    h1(class = "text-center") Builder Info
                    img(class = "mx-auto d-block" src = "images/3.png")
                    p(class = "text-center") Information for builders & builds
                    div(class = "mx-auto w100")
                        div
                            a(href = "https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/109KQbu6A0UVrkOZoqt6pS9Dh5nTXIbbblNlt-sBaLYI/edit#gid=252589615" target = "_blank" class = "header") Builder Spreadsheet
                            ul
                                li Make sure to update this or have a head builder update it for you
                                li Ask an admin to give you access
                            a(href = "http://harmonicraft.com/forum/m/27942449/viewthread/24714837-build-team-central" target = "_blank" class = "header") Builder Forum Post
                            ul
                                li General information about being a builder- must read!
                            
                    br
                    
